<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrīḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tribhuvanakumāravēśyā bhujaṅga Arirājavēśyābhujaṅga Abhinava bhōja</hi>
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">bhujabalarāma bhūpāla vidyādhara raṇaraṅgarākṣasa Uddaṇḍa pratā</hi>
<lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">pa mānamarddana Āsavāra rēvanta śarīrasaṅpatyā sakara trirāyasā</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">rdūla Ayyaṅgamalaparāyaragaṇḍa paramēśvara padakamala paramārādha</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>ka</unclear> gaṇḍagōpāla śiraḥkantukakrīḍāvinōda rāyamīsaragaṇḍa</hi>
<lb n="6" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> darapāṇḍyaku<unclear>mā</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> </hi>
<lb n="7"/><hi rend="grantha">ra pāṇḍyastāpanā</hi><note n="37-1">Incomplete.</note>
</p>

